{"tid":1667072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人講琴晚油麻地有街坊講左句「點解你地蒙面」就中椒同俾狗拉","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:35.000Z","uid":58841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b626bbd036a82ee50cd2f64ab7b56293ac3e2fa","tid":1667072,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"琴晚7點幾8點個陣我咁岩係附近食完野<br />\n等到班狗隻係空地開槍射tg先落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRuG4Sg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRuG4Sg.png&h=2bb09f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後行去尖沙咀方向個陣見到有個灰衫街坊講左標題句野就俾狗咬<br />\n然後有女社工中埋椒<br />\n咁其他街坊見到就係咁屌狗<br />\n其中一隻失控狗隻係咁拎住支閃光燈射記者<br />\n另一隻狗隻上埋實彈<br />\n另一隻拎住cam既狗乸係咁鬧返街坊轉頭<br />\n有時唔係親眼見到都唔知班狗咁撚失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998170124045f61d8db15ca8b44a11a0617c9b76","tid":1667072,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"2a085d700c1d0a0852ef919466b849f03636c332","tid":1667072,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"實彈?!"},{"pid":"fb3f24ad0244db23415ff59077e62edc3e111932","tid":1667072,"uid":217542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"[突發] 北角好似有手足出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 未有報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879a778849095e52d41c5c0bebac443eb23cc2cc","tid":1667072,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"張圖係兩邊都有大批狗隻係度<br />\n一邊射tg<br />\n另一邊開槍<br />\n附近無哂人唔知做乜撚"},{"pid":"9f3d4de9a7d7d586e79e9b4cd5d2b2be